doctemplate (2.4.3.8) raring; urgency=low

  * Add docbook profiling. Set profile params in:
    CUSTOMIZATION/docbook-customization/DOCBOOKPARAMS like this:
     --stringparam profile.userlevel l2
    With that, any elements with a "userlevel" attribute are excluded unless
    their value is l2.
    Examples:
      Included: <sect1 userlevel="l2">
      Excluded: <sect1 userlevel="l3">
      Included: <sect1>

 -- Kyle Nitzsche <kyle.nitzsche@canonical.com>  Thu, 11 Jul 2013 17:19:54 -0400

