doctemplate (2.3) oneiric; urgency=low

  * Make build type argument to doctemplate_make optional if project's
    environment file defines DEFAULT_BUILD. If that is defined and no build
    type arg is passed and $1, use it. In any case, if the build type
    arg is passed, it takes precedence. new projects (doctemplate_create) now
    come with a reasonable or the only default build type set. LP: #922688
  * let po files live in project po/ dir (not in content/po). And let the build
    copy them to content/po (before doing anything else). When projects are
    bzr branches, one should bzr ignore content/po since this will churn
    for no good reason: the real place for po files is po/. LP: #922659
  * delete intermediary "*phase*" files in jumpstart book build. LP: #923812
  * jumpstart book: let build output dir be build/jumpstart (instead of 
    build/jumpstart-book). LP: #922683
  * debian/copyright: changes to bring into conformance with latest spec
  * debian/control: standards version to 3.9.2

