    showdiv functions to toc anchors when dom ready.
  * change expected jquery file name in customization/html-customization to
    jquery.js (instead of expecting a file name that includes the jquery version)
    thus enabling updating to a new jquery version by simply dropping the 
    library file into the custom dir. Note: now making html fails if jquery.js
    is not found, with error message.
