    - Build module  with 'doctemplate_make_html5'
  * add book-html5 project type. Combines html5 project modules into html5 book.
    - Create in pwd with 'doctemplate_setup_book_html5'.
    - Edit 'modules' file to add lines that point at doctemplate html5 projects.
    - Build with doctemplate_make_book_html5
  * html5 modules are free standing and can be remixed into books. To suport this,
    there are rules that govern the div structure of module index.xml files, and
    how to add module-specific link tags to add css and script tags to add javascript.
    These are explained in the module's xml/index.xml file (commented).

